data.title: Doctor Who Season 14 Finale: See plot, when and where to watch in US and UK
data.meta_description: Doctor Who Season 14 concludes with 'Empire of Death' on June 22, 2024, in the UK and June 21, 2024, in the US. The season includes eight episodes of new adventures. Season 15 is confirmed.
data.text:
Synopsis

Doctor Who Season 14 concludes with 'Empire of Death' on June 22, 2024, in the UK and June 21, 2024, in the US. The season includes eight episodes of new adventures. Season 15 is confirmed.

Doctor Who Season 14, featuring Ncuti Gatwa, is coming to an end. The finale episode, 'Empire of Death,' is set to air soon. Here are the details.

Doctor Who Season 14 Finale

Ncuti Gatwa’s debut as the Doctor continues with Season 14. This season is technically Season 40 for long-time fans. It features eight episodes, with new adventures for the Doctor and his companion, Ruby Sunday.

UK Release Date, Time, Where to Watch

The final episode, 'Empire of Death,' will be released in the UK on Saturday, June 22, 2024, at midnight on BBC iPlayer. It will also air on BBC One at 6:40 pm BST on the same day.

When and Where to Watch in US

In the US, Episode 8 will be available on Friday, June 21, 2024, at 7:00 pm ET on Disney+. This season marks the first time Doctor Who has launched on Disney+ with a simultaneous international release.

Finale Episode Plot

The plot for 'Empire of Death' states: "The Doctor has lost, his ageless enemy reigns supreme, and a shadow is falling over creation. Nothing can stop the devastation… except, perhaps, one woman."

Doctor Who Season 15 Confirmation

Season 15 of Doctor Who is confirmed. Filming wrapped in May 2024. It will have eight episodes, featuring Ncuti Gatwa and Millie Gibson, with Russell T Davies returning as showrunner. The release date is expected to be in 2025.

FAQs

When will Doctor Who Season 14 finale air in the UK?

The finale, 'Empire of Death,' will air on June 22, 2024, at midnight on BBC iPlayer and 6:40 pm on BBC One.

When will Doctor Who Season 14 finale air in the US?

The finale, 'Empire of Death,' will be available on June 21, 2024, at 7:00 pm ET on Disney+.
